('bb942d10-83d2-4f46-880d-098f8ec5498e', 'f413f039-fe0f-4120-bdbf-953e2523e694', '4731a2c2-10f2-49e8-af20-c608a69d8072', 'Faced with this, this profile tracks concessions explicitly and matches them one-for-one, never more, and true to form is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into stoic freeze — that resolves almost before it registers.', 0.73, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('84ce7ef2-57f6-49cf-9517-6f98c573fad1', 'a2607082-2f22-4cae-a28f-10a5469b44d8', 'c81a1b45-92b5-472e-be50-1c6fc270508c', 'Faced with this, this type lets the numbers set the floor and refuses to negotiate against itself, and true to form lets the first number on the table quietly set the whole range.', 'Treats the choice as a small research problem: gather the knowable facts first, model the downside, then commit only once the math stops moving. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'A flat, measured pulse with no real spike, resolving into stoic freeze — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.75, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b332d20e-e57d-4ae1-9c89-89f62b96a7ae', 'ff198c5f-777c-41a1-9775-ccaf7311da15', '05b047a2-8d50-4327-9e0d-db766ceb5fb8', 'Faced with this, this type stays silent past the point of discomfort, letting the other side fill the gap, and true to form assumes the bad statistic applies to other people.', 'Treats a rushed decision as a defect regardless of outcome, and resists pressure to shortcut the process. The relationship and the number are both on the table at once.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into relief capitulation — that never really rises to the level of a feeling at all.', 0.71, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6b193d33-fa15-46be-8307-36af60d46ff5', '10f05559-e318-4dff-8f0f-3c01f412cfab', 'fe4ea815-f658-409a-9299-3331e5aba395', 'Faced with this, the individual tracks concessions explicitly and matches them one-for-one, never more, and true to form underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 'Revisits the same decision from a new angle each time doubt resurfaces, even after nominally deciding. Every option here also has to survive the other side''s reaction.', 'Barely a ripple of concern, resolving into relief capitulation — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.85, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
