('2bb51623-d801-4a33-b110-0766ae6f8df2', '293fa221-d6e0-4bd5-8df7-9f954c22402e', '678735b3-9798-45d4-8a53-4decbef6f7a4', 'Faced with this, this profile executes the pre-committed plan exactly, resisting the urge to improvise under pressure, and true to form never quite escapes the first figure it heard, however arbitrary.', 'Builds an explicit decision matrix for a call most people would make on instinct, and defers to whichever option scores highest even if it feels wrong. The numbers on the screen are the only feedback that matters here.', 'The faintest tightening, gone as soon as it is noticed, resolving into stoic freeze — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.72, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f42ffbf9-3cfd-4b8f-95c9-e481a0d911dc', '18cd33a6-3fd3-41e2-97c4-373256bd838b', '1346fd84-606e-4efe-9889-15378744a67f', 'Faced with this, the individual acts on the first strong feeling, hitting the button before the reasoning fully forms, and true to form discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 'Lets urgency substitute for analysis, converting pressure directly into action. The numbers on the screen are the only feedback that matters here.', 'A hot flash of panic before any thought forms, resolving into panic selling — that leaves a residue of vigilance well past the event itself.', 0.58, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('90500b95-397f-4a07-8207-f3f756d1d8cb', 'd1d12c02-c976-424f-9062-061f27fdfedd', 'ff3132e1-89ba-482d-a8fb-f819065a38d7', 'Faced with this, this profile presses the position further, treating the volatility itself as the opportunity, and true to form takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 'Feels the decision settle before it is fully articulated, and moves on that settling rather than waiting for certainty. Price action does not care which argument feels more convincing.', 'A quick surge of adrenaline that fades as fast as it came, resolving into righteous anger — that resolves as soon as there is something concrete to act on.', 0.6, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c740fecd-05e2-44d1-97b9-61c4bcd43934', 'f8714b85-6531-4127-bbe6-59f1a7f22c98', '678735b3-9798-45d4-8a53-4decbef6f7a4', 'Faced with this, this profile de-risks well before the textbook signal, uncomfortable holding exposure into the unknown, and true to form would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.', 'Weighs its own instinct as only one input among several trusted others, and defers when they disagree. The numbers on the screen are the only feedback that matters here.', 'A brief flicker of tension, resolving into fomo buying — that dissolves quickly once the ambiguity clears.', 0.59, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('97f38b88-67a2-4d1d-b548-c78ad0505ba8', '6bd8cc47-6d67-4bdc-aa06-d6f2db3469dc', '2ee80af3-2a1d-46a5-80cd-6e2d65b600e1', 'Faced with this, this profile treats the moment as one more data point for a system, not an exception to react to, and true to form never quite escapes the first figure it heard, however arbitrary.', 'Distrusts the first plausible-sounding answer and keeps testing alternatives until one survives every objection raised against it. Price action does not care which argument feels more convincing.', 'Almost no visible reaction at all, resolving into euphoric overreach — that leaves no discernible trace once the moment passes.', 0.67, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bb1ea5ea-2ea9-4f00-8a2f-246176a20f40', '5612e1aa-a5e1-4315-a050-ff00ec8eb5d7', '3d421411-9f4d-45d4-ad25-936b4bb718e3', 'Faced with this, this person presses the position further, treating the volatility itself as the opportunity, and true to form cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap.', 'Prefers a decisive wrong turn to an open-ended maybe, and corrects course later if it has to. This time the variable is money moving in real time.', 'A noticeable but manageable spike of unease, resolving into righteous anger — that settles once the choice is made.', 0.57, '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
